# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# LangGraph Travel Planner — 全局环境变量 (docker-compose 用)
# 复制为 backend/.env: cp .env.example backend/.env
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ── LLM (必填) ──
LLM_MODEL=deepseek-chat
LLM_BASE_URL=https://api.deepseek.com
LLM_API_KEY=your-api-key-here      # ← 必填

# ── PostgreSQL ──
# docker-compose 自建 PG (默认):
POSTGRES_URI=postgresql://travel_user:travel_pass_2026@localhost:5432/travel_planner
POSTGRES_PASSWORD=travel_pass_2026
# 外部 PG 实例时修改:
# POSTGRES_URI=postgresql://postgres:yourpassword@your-host:5432/your_database

# ── 高德 Web 服务 (地图/天气/POI/路线；留空时使用 Mock 降级) ──
AMAP_API_KEY=
AMAP_BASE_URL=https://restapi.amap.com
PROVIDER_TIMEOUT_SECONDS=8
PROVIDER_CACHE_TTL_SECONDS=3600
WEATHER_CACHE_TTL_SECONDS=1800

# ── JWT Auth (必改!) ──
JWT_SECRET_KEY=change-me-in-production-use-a-random-string
JWT_EXPIRE_HOURS=24

# ── LangSmith (可选) ──
# LANGSMITH_API_KEY=your-langsmith-key
# LANGSMITH_PROJECT=langgraph-travel-planner
# LANGCHAIN_TRACING_V2=true

# ── Server ──
HOST=0.0.0.0
PORT=8000

# ── Frontend ──
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:8000
